song.title: Junkie 2149 (Byproduct remix)
song.info:
Timbral was playing a cool oldschool live set at Evoke 2010. I liked it quite a bit, so I had to go and download some more of his music from the net. A 2010 live set of his had this strangely named, fun and catchy tune that started playing in my head every now and then.
When you play a chiptune in your head, at some point your imagination kind of starts adding elements to it, breaking the technical limitations of the original chip. (Or that's what happens to me anyway.) Eventually I decided I might as well compose this remix in FL Studio and play it from the speakers instead of just the brain. Here you go.
